Sure, should I #[ignore] the test so we can merge this and add a note in there to un-ignore it when fixed?

jameysharp commented on issue #5629:

I don't have a preference either way. If you don't want to keep an open PR around I think it's fine to merge it #[ignore]d, but I think it's also fine to just leave this PR here until the underlying issue is sorted out.
